{
  "texts": [
    "This gives higher values to terms that connect strongly to many terms in the same topic and are thus most representative of that topic.",
    "Once the filtering and ordering is complete, the set of topics is returned to the user.",
    "Topic HierarchyThis basic formulation of CT produces a set of topics like vanilla LDA.",
    "However, there exists a natural structure to the graph representation and it is straightforward to adapt CT to return a hierarchy.",
    "By taking advantage of the community structure generated on the graph or the community detection algorithm, it is possible very simply to obtain a hierarchy of topics."
  ]
}